#: ../../docs/classes/class_spotlight.rst:17
msgid "Description"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/classes/class_spotlight.rst:19
msgid ""
"A Spotlight is a type of :ref:`Light <class_Light>` node that emits "
"lights in a specific direction, in the shape of a cone. The light is "
"attenuated through the distance. This attenuation can be configured by "
"changing the energy, radius and attenuation parameters of :ref:`Light "
"<class_Light>`."
msgstr ""

